title: Tom Segura
itunes:title: Tom Segura
description: My HoneyDew this week is the King of YMH, Tom Segura! Tom returns to talk about his overdose on GHB when he was in college and the rehab that followed. We also talk about a recent incident where he took a mega-dose from Joey Diaz on a flight, and one of the dirtiest football plays of his life. Tom wraps up with advice to his 16 year old self. This was such a fun episode!
